{"tid":2218406,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"稱各人已選兩律師 李家超被揭講大話","createTime":"2020-09-26T07:32:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T07:51:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e8a1024a68a34b8d6a4a975f2d6920eb4901bc68","tid":2218406,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T07:32:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200926/CJXT2QZJRZAIHDECTFRLHCR6YU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200926%2FCJXT2QZJRZAIHDECTFRLHCR6YU%2F&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTu85RZDHrhPshgzcG8Nqr5vw%3D&h=47e01565\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200926%2FCJXT2QZJRZAIHDECTFRLHCR6YU%2F&h=d22eb890\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200926/CJXT2QZJRZAIHDECTFRLHCR6YU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n稱各人已選兩律師 李家超被揭講大話<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/34HX5c_9teKs0QmccQx38RsKs5Y=/1620x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NXU4BPEV3ZGYLIHMRFPYATIDRM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F34HX5c_9teKs0QmccQx38RsKs5Y%3D%2F1620x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNXU4BPEV3ZGYLIHMRFPYATIDRM.jpg&h=893457e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■李家超日前指12人已各自揀選了兩名代表律師。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】受「12港人」之一張銘裕家屬委託的律師第二度到深圳要求會見被拒。他昨午帶公證到鹽田看守所尋求探視，結果與此前所有律師一樣，被告知當事人已委託了兩個律師。目前已有10名律師尋求探視被拒。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：再多一人被頒拘捕令<br />\n<br />\n該名律師代表21歲學生張銘裕。消息指，看守所職員在審核文件後，告知律師當事人已有律師，而且都是由本人委託的，「不是指定的」。....................................................。律師當時質疑，當局謊稱嚴已委託了兩名律師，是要阻止家屬委託的律師介入。<br />\n<br />\n本報昨向保安局查詢，局方回應稱據駐粵辦向當局了解，12名疑犯現時身體狀況良好，並已各自委任了兩名律師。............................<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：警拒批10.1遊行 民陣擬上訴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再有律師被逼退<br />\n<br />\n另外據了解，受家屬委託的律師持續遭施壓。過去兩日再有至少五名律師被司法局或國保約談，要求律師退出案件，包括兩位近日前往鹽田看守所的律師，會見不果後都立即被約談。有新接手案件的律師，連委託書都未收到，就已接到司法局的電話，懷疑是在香港辦理公證的環節洩露身份，令當局有機會在律師辦妥手續前將律師截下，.........................<br />\n<br />\n也有律師已多次被約談，當局由一開始只要求律師備案，後到勸退，到現在已強硬要求律師退出。多名受壓的律師堅拒退出案件，表示一日有律師守着這個位置，當局一日都會如坐針氈，能堅持一會兒是一會兒。"},{"pid":"d852dec92081bd5a1b262d9b8641ee4a157f5cc4","tid":2218406,"uid":266294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T07:33:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0989ec34b0bbcc0ab3e736becd228f47507d20b9","tid":2218406,"uid":254383,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T07:34:31.000Z","msg":"狗官邊句唔係大話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97862987427d5eeb363a6f6ce8aee8e839d33d5d","tid":2218406,"uid":115579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T07:37:32.000Z","msg":"呢班畜生有講過真話？"},{"pid":"834ed8edd69579f7be5a00342a01ae13fdd91788","tid":2218406,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T07:51:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}